<i>everything around you,</i>

448
01:01:50,307 --> 01:01:53,275
<i>until the only thing</i>
<i>that is left</i>

449
01:01:53,277 --> 01:01:54,576
<i>is the calm.</i>

450
01:01:54,578 --> 01:01:56,178
<i>Now open your eyes.</i>

451
01:01:56,180 --> 01:01:59,281
( Leon breathing
raggedly )

452
01:02:01,117 --> 01:02:02,117
( Silence )

453
01:02:02,119 --> 01:02:05,620
<i>- Leon, are you there?</i>
- ( Exhales shakily )

454
01:02:05,622 --> 01:02:08,590
- <i>Is everything okay?</i>
<i>-</i> Yeah.

455
01:02:08,592 --> 01:02:10,659
<i>Good. Now listen,</i>
<i>it's late,</i>

456
01:02:10,661 --> 01:02:14,229
<i>and I really need</i>
<i>to get some rest.</i>

457
01:02:14,231 --> 01:02:15,397
Okay.

458
01:02:15,399 --> 01:02:17,632
<i>So no more calls, okay?</i>

459
01:02:17,634 --> 01:02:19,301
No.

460
01:02:19,303 --> 01:02:21,369
<i>Good night, Leon.</i>

461
01:02:21,371 --> 01:02:24,639
Yeah, good night.
Thank you.

462
01:03:58,668 --> 01:04:01,536
( Exhales heavily )

463
01:04:19,822 --> 01:04:23,225
( Low growling )

464
01:04:33,936 --> 01:04:38,907
( Floorboards creak,
growling continues )

465
01:05:26,389 --> 01:05:29,858
( Growling )

466
01:05:39,368 --> 01:05:44,406
( Growling and ferocious
pounding on door )

467
01:06:07,630 --> 01:06:10,398
( Loud bang )

468
01:06:10,967 --> 01:06:13,335
( Exclaims )

469
01:06:16,906 --> 01:06:20,842
( Growling
and snorting )

470
01:06:25,648 --> 01:06:27,716
( Ferocious loud growl )

471
01:06:42,865 --> 01:06:45,367
Mother: <i>Leon.</i>

472
01:07:24,707 --> 01:07:27,175
<i>Believe.</i>

473
01:07:27,177 --> 01:07:29,778
No.

474
01:07:36,085 --> 01:07:39,587
- <i>Believe.</i>
- No!

475
01:07:47,830 --> 01:07:49,664
<i>Believe.</i>

476
01:07:50,833 --> 01:07:52,834
No.

477
01:07:54,003 --> 01:07:56,805
I don't believe it.

478
01:09:22,691 --> 01:09:24,025
( Phone ringing )

479
01:09:24,027 --> 01:09:26,861
<i>Tribal trade.</i>
<i>Bill Phillips here.</i>

480
01:09:26,863 --> 01:09:28,930
Bill, it's Leon.

481
01:09:28,932 --> 01:09:32,167
<i>Leon?</i>
<i>What time is it?</i>

482
01:09:32,169 --> 01:09:34,569
I wanna sell everything.

483
01:09:34,571 --> 01:09:36,004
I want it all gone.

484
01:09:36,006 --> 01:09:37,772
I'll send you
a full inventory

485
01:09:37,774 --> 01:09:39,741
in a couple of days.

486
01:09:39,743 --> 01:09:43,044
<i>Um... yeah.</i>
<i>Sure.</i>

487
01:09:43,046 --> 01:09:47,248
Okay? Thanks.
Sorry for waking you up.

488
01:10:40,069 --> 01:10:42,904
<i>Don't go.</i>

489
01:10:46,909 --> 01:10:51,145
<i>There's so much</i>
<i>i want to say to you.</i>

490
01:10:51,147 --> 01:10:56,251
<i>So much</i>
<i>i need to explain.</i>

491
01:10:57,219 --> 01:11:01,322
<i>I waited so long</i>
<i>for you to come back.</i>

492
01:11:01,324 --> 01:11:06,394
<i>I waited so long.</i>

493
01:11:08,297 --> 01:11:13,835
<i>Until I realized</i>
<i>you never would.</i>

494
01:11:14,169 --> 01:11:20,742
<i>That night, I saw</i>
<i>something through the window,</i>

495
01:11:20,744 --> 01:11:24,646
<i>and I told myself</i>

496
01:11:24,648 --> 01:11:27,348
<i>it was just a cat.</i>

497
01:11:27,350 --> 01:11:32,186
<i>I tried to occupy myself,</i>

498
01:11:32,188 --> 01:11:34,956
<i>but I was afraid.</i>

499
01:11:34,958 --> 01:11:40,128
<i>I could feel it</i>
<i>watching me.</i>

500
01:11:40,130 --> 01:11:44,098
<i>I wanted to talk to you</i>
<i>to tell you</i>

501
01:11:44,100 --> 01:11:46,367
<i>that I'd made a mistake,</i>

502
01:11:46,369 --> 01:11:48,903
<i>that you were</i>
<i>more important to me</i>

503
01:11:48,905 --> 01:11:52,874
<i>than anything else</i>
<i>in the world.</i>

504
01:11:52,876 --> 01:11:57,312
<i>But my thoughts</i>
<i>were confused,</i>

505
01:11:57,314 --> 01:12:00,214
<i>and I kept thinking</i>

506
01:12:00,216 --> 01:12:05,987
<i>it was too big</i>
<i>to be a cat.</i>

507
01:12:11,393 --> 01:12:15,830
<i>That's when I realized</i>
<i>what I'd been trying to ignore</i>

508
01:12:15,832 --> 01:12:18,966
<i>for so long.</i>

509
01:12:18,968 --> 01:12:24,038
<i>That you had turned</i>
<i>your back on me.</i>

510
01:12:25,741 --> 01:12:29,110
<i>That you abandoned me.</i>

511
01:12:30,112 --> 01:12:33,748
<i>That you</i>
<i>no longer cared.</i>

512
01:12:35,084 --> 01:12:42,890
<i>That my little angel</i>
<i>would no longer protect me.</i>

513
01:12:42,892 --> 01:12:44,225
( Gasping )

514
01:12:44,227 --> 01:12:47,762
<i>And when faith is gone...</i>

515
01:12:49,231 --> 01:12:55,203
<i>Loneliness can be</i>
<i>a monster.</i>

516
01:13:26,135 --> 01:13:30,037
<i>I thought you would</i>
<i>come to me then.</i>

517
01:13:31,407 --> 01:13:34,342
<i>But you never did.</i>

518
01:13:40,015 --> 01:13:48,289
<i>The funeral</i>
<i>was empty without you.</i>

519
01:13:55,264 --> 01:13:57,532
<i>The loneliness</i>
<i>is worse now</i>

520
01:13:57,534 --> 01:14:00,334
<i>than it ever was.</i>

521
01:14:03,539 --> 01:14:09,243
<i>And all I can do</i>
<i>is remember</i>

522
01:14:09,245 --> 01:14:12,146
<i>the way you were,</i>

523
01:14:12,148 --> 01:14:16,250
<i>and make believe.</i>

524
01:14:16,252 --> 01:14:22,056
<i>Make believe that</i>
<i>you came looking for me.</i>

525
01:14:22,058 --> 01:14:27,094
<i>Make believe</i>
<i>that you felt.</i>

526
01:14:27,963 --> 01:14:32,133
<i>Make believe</i>
<i>that you hoped.</i>

527
01:14:32,135 --> 01:14:38,239
<i>Make believe</i>
<i>that you remembered.</i>

528
01:14:38,241 --> 01:14:43,010
<i>Remembered that</i>
<i>the soul lives on</i>

529
01:14:43,012 --> 01:14:44,846
<i>long after death,</i>

530
01:14:44,848 --> 01:14:51,118
<i>eternally,</i>
<i>and without end.</i>

531
01:14:54,156 --> 01:14:57,992
<i>Make believe that</i>
<i>you cared.</i>

532
01:15:01,430 --> 01:15:05,399
<i>Make believe that</i>
<i>you miss me...</i>

533
01:15:07,202 --> 01:15:11,906
<i>As much as</i>
<i>i miss you.</i>

534
01:15:14,443 --> 01:15:20,047
( Operatic vocalizing )

